Once upon a time in a forest where lived a monkey on a berry tree which was on the banks of a river.
In the same forest,where lived a crocodile and his wife.One day,the crocodile came to the banks of the river and rested under the tree.
The kind hearted monkey offerd him some fruit.The crocodile came back for same fruits as he loved them.
As days passed by,The crocodile and monkey became good friends.